recipes.title: Bengali Vorta Updated
recipes.description:
Updated There are so many nights when I wish I had some random dinner ideas to look at for dinner inspiration! I have a list of our favorite recipes but I like to new dinner ideas and make easy dinners based on what I have in my house that I can make with pantry staples.

I wanted to throw together a list of recipes that you can peek at and find random dinner ideas. Some of them are made in the instant pot and other recipes are made in the slow cooker.
